---
<Section>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col w-fullpt-20 my-auto font-medium mx-auto text-center md:text-left lg:w-1/2 lg:pb-10"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-main-titles">Hola! Soy Ander</h1>
